_:N55534f36534e4bac97f2c0e6d0d10a81 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Dame Clare Barclay DBE is President of Enterprise and Industry <abbr title=\"Europe, the Middle East and Africa\">EMEA</abbr> at Microsoft, appointed in November 2024. Prior to this Clare spent 4 years as <abbr title=\"Chief Executive Officer\">CEO</abbr> of Microsoft UK, leading through a period of significant transformation and growth. She is responsible for driving Microsoft’s growth ambitions and driving <abbr title=\"artificial intelligence\">AI</abbr> industry innovation across the UK, Europe, Middle East and Africa.</p>\n\n<p>With nearly 3 decades in industry, Clare has held a range of senior leadership roles with experience across all aspects of the business, including partnerships to unlock opportunity across industries and empowering small and medium-sized businesses. She has driven significant transformational change for Microsoft and is passionate about the importance of skills and helping young people thrive in tech careers across industries.</p>\n\n<p>Clare was made a Dame Commander of the Order of the British Empire in the King’s Birthday Honours 2025 for services to Business, Technology, and Leadership.</p>\n\n" .
_:N55534f36534e4bac97f2c0e6d0d10a81 <http://schema.org/name> "Dame Clare Barclay DBE" .
